text.tspan: We all know that auto insurance protects us if our vehicle suffers
costly damage, but did you know that a vehicle service contract
can protect us if our vehicle suffers a costly breakdown?
Minuteman VSC offers vehicle service contracts (VSCs) from
top-rated providers at a fraction of the price charged at a car
dealership. We also offer you reputable payment plan providers
that can allow you to purchase your VSC at 0% interest with no
credit check.
To learn more about the VSC and payment plan providers we offer,
please visit the Our Partners page.
Minuteman VSC is not the administrator or payment plan provider
for the VSC you purchase and has no obligation with regards to
your VSC. If you have already used our service to purchase a
VSC, you should have received your signed contracts via email that
name your administrator and your payment plan provider.
If you have a question or claim concerning your vehicle service
contract or payment plan contract, we encourage you to contact
the respective provider directly.
If your vehicle service contract provider or payment plan provider
is not responsive to your questions, or if you have a question and
you are not sure whom to ask, feel free to reach out to us:
Don’t let a vehicle
breakdown cost you
a fortune.
Let
Minuteman VSC
help get you protected in minutes.

g.text: Where You Can Buy a Vehicle Service Contract

text.tspan: Sea Pine Technologies LLC, including its successors and assigns, operating
under the trade names “Service Lane VSC” and “Minuteman VSC” (hereinafter
referred to as “we,” “our” and “us”), offersconsumers (hereinafter referred to
as “you” and “your”) the ability, through your use of our technology platform,
to receive free quotes for vehicle service contracts (“VSC” or “VSCs”) and
purchase VSCs online. IMPORTANT: We are not a party to any contract with
you. This platform is intended solely for the purpose of providing quotes from
VSC providers and allowing you to purchase the VSC you choose. All VSCs
offered for sale through this site are underwritten by reputable third party VSC
providers. TheVSC provider you choose will be very apparent to you before
you finalize the transaction and make your payment.
